Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.54,0:00:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Cutie Mark Crusaders!\NCutie Mark Crusaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.21,0:00:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Cutie Mark Crusaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.91,0:00:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Cutie Mark Crusaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.44,0:00:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Scootaloo: We're at my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I got my cutie mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.85,0:00:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.05,0:00:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great, Skeedaddle!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.82,0:00:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! What's it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.59,0:00:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Knot tying!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.02,0:00:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And I never would've gotten\Nit without all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.52,0:00:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we suggest\Nknot-tying?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.19,0:00:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I tried sailing,\Nlike you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.66,0:00:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, I tried fishing,\Nlike YOU said.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.13,0:00:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I tried rowing, like\Nyou said. But my oar broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.74,0:00:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So I used my fishing line\Nto tie it back together...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,AND I GOT MY CUTIE MARK!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.21,0:00:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,AHH! I can't wait to tell EVERYPONY!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.78,0:00:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!\NYeah!\NWoohoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.85,0:00:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[Australian accent]\NOh, how exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.11,0:00:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You three truly have a\Ngift for helping ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.75,0:00:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, thanks, Aunt Holiday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.55,0:00:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not sure we can\Ntake credit for this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.26,0:00:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.66,0:00:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You encouraged that\Ncolt to try new things.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.79,0:01:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And because you all believed\Nin him, he succeeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I could use that kind of help... Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.52,0:01:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Auntie Lofty. You\Nalready HAVE your cutie mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.74,0:01:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Lot of good it does me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.91,0:01:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't decide what\Ntheme to give this quilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.81,0:01:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. I've run out of inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.75,0:01:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How about apples?\NPuppies? Kites!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.38,0:01:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Or cotton candy? Or ballet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.35,0:01:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What about a Wonderbolt quilt?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.88,0:01:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha! See? Leave\Nit to you three
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.19,0:01:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to come up with more ideas\Nthan I've had in a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.92,0:01:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's talent!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.59,0:01:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness, we'd better get going
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.06,0:01:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,or we'll miss our train home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.60,0:01:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I left you plenty of healthy\Nfood for the weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.60,0:01:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And {\i1}I{\i0} left you cookies. Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The Cakes will stay with\Nyou tonight, then Rarity,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.01,0:01:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and Rainbow Dash after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.11,0:01:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, we're just a\Nfew stops from Ponyville
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.34,0:01:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,if you need us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.18,0:01:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She knows, Holiday! See\Nyou next week, slugger.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.62,0:01:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, Aunt Holiday!\NBye, Auntie Lofty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.49,0:02:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Your aunts are so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.92,0:02:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It's really\Ncool they watch you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.99,0:02:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,while your parents are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.63,0:02:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! I just wish\Nthey lived closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.73,0:02:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Nopony bakes like Auntie Lofty..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.97,0:02:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] They're coming home today!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.61,0:02:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,MY PARENTS!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we're going to learn
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.81,0:03:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,about the Pegasus\NWeather Factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Once everypony is\Nin their seats...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The factory specializes in\Nsnow, rain, sunshine, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.80,0:03:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem! Scootaloo. May\NI help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I.. just noticed your\Nerasers needed dusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we hold off on the\Nlesson until after lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How about show and tell?\NDoes anypony have any...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My parents are coming\Nhome to Ponyville today!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. They don't live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.85,0:03:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. Their jobs are way\Ntoo important for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They travel to the farthest,\Nmost dangerous places
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.73,0:03:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,in Equestria to study unknown\Nplants and fierce creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:03:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And what they learn helps\Npony science and medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd go with them, but\Nit's TOO dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.31,0:04:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Once, my mom had to\Nwing-wrestle a wyvern!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And my dad got trapped\Nin a chimera's cave
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.11,0:04:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,for three moons! He still\Nhas the scars to prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.09,0:04:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Pffft!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.15,0:04:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making that up.\NNopony has THAT kind of job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.57,0:04:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a CRAGADILE!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.53,0:04:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [action music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy there, Marshmallow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.98,0:04:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Time you were in your\Ncrate for your nap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.69,0:04:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And that means now, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:04:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom! Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Still think she's\Nmakin' it all up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nuh-uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony, meet my parents:\NSnap Shutter and Mane Allgood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh. Sorry to make such an entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.51,0:05:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Just brought back a few mates\Nfrom our last adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.68,0:05:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't wait another\Nmoment to see Scootaloo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we didn't\Ninterrupt anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I... think\Nclass is dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Crikey! You're nearly as\Ntall as me now, Scoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.40,0:05:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, c'mon, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.97,0:05:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Scootaloo. We missed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too, Mom! Did you\Nget all my letters?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.31,0:05:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And read them twenty times!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're never as\Ngood as the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.98,0:05:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.92,0:05:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I say we celebrate\Nwith ice cream sundaes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't have THOSE in the\Njungle, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you all\Ncome? Our treat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.56,0:06:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And Princess Twilight said
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.93,0:06:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,we're such good\Nfriendship tutors,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,she might even let\Nus TEACH a class!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Good on ya, Scoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What an honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can give you a tour of\Nthe school if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, if you're staying\Nfor a while this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.01,0:06:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you'll be\Nseeing plenty of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.25,0:06:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.21,0:06:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm hm. Because we've\Ntaken a new job assignment
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that will let ALL\Nof us live together!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe\Nit! That's AWESOME!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.79,0:06:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right,\NScootaloo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.58,0:06:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Woo hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We never planned to be away for\Nso long in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We just kept discovering things
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.53,0:06:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that could help\NEquestria, and nopony else
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.07,0:06:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,had the experience\Nto finish our job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.64,0:06:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But with all that's happened\Nlately: Sombra's return,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.47,0:06:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the destruction of\Nthe Tree of Harmony,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,we decided our family\Nshould be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the best day of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.48,0:06:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll stay in town\Nfor the weekend
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.15,0:06:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,so you can pack\Nyour things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.45,0:06:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...WHAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.22,0:07:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all moving\Nto Shirelanka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.66,0:07:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where our\Nnew job is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But...my friends\Nare in Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You can come back\Nand visit 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Or they can take the train to\Nus. There's one every month.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.77,0:07:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But Scootaloo can't leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.67,0:07:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been together\Nour whole lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a big\Nchange for everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But it'll be a good change!\NGive it time; you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.34,0:07:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,is the end of the\NCutie Mark Crusaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.32,0:07:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I now call our last ever
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.66,0:07:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Cutie Mark Crusader\Nmeeting to order.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,First item of business, cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't let the blank flanks\Ndown just cause I'm gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.18,0:08:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta keep being\NCMCs without me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.92,0:08:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[sniff] How!? There's only two of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you can find\Na replacement for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we can't!\NYou're the only.. YOU!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothin's gonna be the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's gonna ride their scooter\Nahead of us everywhere we go!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.07,0:08:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Or... or put on plays with us!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.67,0:08:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Or go camping with us!? Or\Njust...hang out with us!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.64,0:08:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's worse for me! I have\Nto say goodbye to BOTH OF-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess who just got\Nthree front-row tickets
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.52,0:08:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,to the Wonderbolts\Nshow next week?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, that is NOT the\Nreaction I was expecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.69,0:08:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[sniffles] Thanks for the tickets,\NRainbow Dash. But I can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.93,0:08:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Her parents are making her move
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,super far away from Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What!? No way!\NScootaloo belongs HERE!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:09:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And now we'll probably never\Nsee her again! It's HOPELESS!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.38,0:09:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa whoa whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot believe you're\Ngiving up so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.18,0:09:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the Cutie\NMark Crusaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.72,0:09:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Solving tough problems\Nis what you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.02,0:09:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We are pretty good at\Ncoming up with ideas...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! When we work\Ntogether, we're unstoppable!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe we didn't\Nthink of it before!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.40,0:09:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's list time, y'all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.14,0:09:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,First question,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.14,0:09:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,why do Scootaloo's parents\Nwant to move to Shirelanka?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.87,0:09:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where their new job is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] What if we get\Nthem a job HERE instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.15,0:09:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! They like dangerous\Ncreatures, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.32,0:09:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta have some\Nof those around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.42,0:09:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Like... Timberwolves!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.45,0:09:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad knows all about those. And\Ncockatrices, and bugbears...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They only study\Nsuper-rare animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Then maybe we need to\Ngive them an animal
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.43,0:09:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,nopony's ever heard of!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh.. then how would\N{\i1}we{\i0} hear about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:10:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we're\Nmaking it up! C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.27,0:10:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So... you want these\Ntickets, or...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.14,0:10:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what I\Nwanted to show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The tracks of the {\i1}mysterious{\i0}\NEverfree Banshee Beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.52,0:10:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, they're like\Nnothing I've ever seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.46,0:10:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Legend says it has five\Nclaws and three wings,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's super-dangerous\Nif you get close.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.76,0:10:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If only somepony\Ncould prove it exists..!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.80,0:10:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. Easy enough. We'll\Nfollow the spoor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.27,0:10:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.31,0:10:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I heard\Nsomething this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.68,0:10:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [mysterious music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.86,0:10:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So the plan is, we\Nlet 'em get a picture,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:10:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,then we hide again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.66,0:11:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah..!\N[shutter clicks]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.63,0:11:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the plan is.. RUN!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[snap]\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.08,0:11:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh-heh. Guess you\Nsolved the mystery...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd better get back.\NThere's a lot to get ready
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,before the house goes\Nup for sale tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.16,0:11:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Scootaloo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a NEW plan to\Nkeep you in Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.33,0:11:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We just gotta show your\Nparents we're a set of three!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they'll have to let\Nyou stay here with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.95,0:11:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Scoot? Are these yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Thanks, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.92,0:12:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sending them to\Nthe Pony Book of Records.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the only three\Nponies in Equestria
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,with the SAME\Ncutie mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The chances of that\Nare so rare,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.30,0:12:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,it means we belong\Ntogether, forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but you {\i1}don't{\i0} have\Nthe same cutie mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, sure we do! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.27,0:12:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this part is the same,\Nbut the picture inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,each of these is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.38,0:12:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it means you'll\Nstay best friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.21,0:12:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter where you go.\NAnd that's really special.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,0:12:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But...we... How do\Nyou argue with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, y'all. Time to\Ntake things up a notch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.47,0:12:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,With prune juice?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.34,0:12:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a potion I mixed\Nup from Zecora's book!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Prune is only ONE\Nof the ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.14,0:13:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,On this potion, please\Ndepend. Any separation, mend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Friends together till the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We just gotta dab a\Nlittle on our hooves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.89,0:13:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds perfect, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.52,0:13:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Better than perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.32,0:13:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something supposed to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.94,0:13:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is THIS the something\Nthat's supposed to happen!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.67,0:13:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The book didn't really say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for trying,\NApple Bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.98,0:13:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But I might as\Nwell face it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna have to\Nleave Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up, Scootaloo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.95,0:13:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This just gave me\Nan even BETTER idea
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.85,0:13:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,how to keep you\Nhere. C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.29,0:13:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.06,0:13:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we'd better see Zecora\Nabout fixing this first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.67,0:13:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We're running out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.84,0:14:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This HAS to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.14,0:14:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Scootaloo? I know you're\Nhaving fun with your friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.95,0:14:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but we need to get all our\Nthings to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.55,0:14:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't miss tomorrow's train.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only one for a month!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.82,0:14:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you'll just have\Nto go without me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.59,0:14:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm staying with the CMCs!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We are chained to this post!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And nuthin' and nopony is\Ngonna move us, no matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.90,0:14:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...what.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We just sold the house, Scoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this is hard\Nto accept, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.34,0:14:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more than\Nhard! It's NOT FAIR!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.41,0:14:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making me pick between\Nmy family and my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.82,0:14:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Scootaloo. Moving\Naway won't stop you three
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,from caring about each other.\NWhy don't you sleep over
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.95,0:14:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,with Sweetie Belle and\NApple Bloom tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll give you a chance\Nto say a real goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.73,0:14:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't WANT to say goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.96,0:14:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're changing my whole life
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:15:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,without even asking how I FEEL!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.61,0:15:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Scootaloo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.05,0:15:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,To stay with my aunts.\NYou heard my parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't another train\Nto Shirelanka for a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.95,0:15:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm not on it, they'll\Nhave to go without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.56,0:15:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we're comin' with ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.09,0:15:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure? I don't want\Nto get you in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.96,0:15:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity won't be mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.06,0:15:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack neither!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.40,0:15:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet she'd do the same\Nthing for her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the best, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.97,0:15:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,WE'RE the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] Scootaloo! What a nice surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've got a surprise for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.96,0:16:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You three inspired me\Nto finish my quilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,See? It's Cutie Mark\NCrusader themed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.93,0:16:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We love hearing stories about\Nall the ponies you've helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.20,0:16:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So Lofty decided to celebrate\Nthe special job you three do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.01,0:16:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's.. still a work\Nin progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.88,0:16:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not your quilt we're\Nsad about, Auntie Lofty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom and Dad are back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.68,0:16:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're making me move\Nto Shirelanka with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.15,0:16:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Snap and Mane are back?\NThey didn't tell me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.19,0:16:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. I think the\Nmailpony delivered
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.13,0:16:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,your letter to my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.86,0:16:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I love my family! But I love\Nbeing with my friends, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.57,0:16:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to have to choose...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, why\Ndon't your parents
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.24,0:16:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,just stay in Ponyville?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Their job is too important...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.08,0:16:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.31,0:16:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this another\Npotion idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.41,0:16:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Scootaloo's parents are\Nthe only ponies in Equestria
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.22,0:16:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that can do what they do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Right..?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, so are we! Our\Ncutie marks prove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.43,0:17:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Our job is to help other\Nponies find their purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And nopony else can do that!\NSo, if my parents split us up,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.03,0:17:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it'd be just as bad as\Nthem quitting their jobs!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Woohoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.41,0:17:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now.. how do we\Nexplain that to 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.84,0:17:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, {\i1}you{\i0} don't have\Nto explain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.95,0:17:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,THEY will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.12,0:17:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Feeling better, Scootaloo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A little. I just wanna show\Nyou something before we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.06,0:17:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, but let's make it\Nswift. That train won't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.73,0:17:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet Celestia's\Nslippers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mane: What is all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Cutie Mark Crusader\NAppreciation Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But we couldn't start\Nwithout ALL of them here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,CMCs! CMCs! CMCs!\NCMCs! CMCs! CMCs!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,These three ponies\Nshare a rare ability
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,to help others find\Ntheir true purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.96,0:18:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a job only they can\Ndo, and only together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.60,0:18:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In honor of all\Nthey have done
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.73,0:18:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and continue to do for\Nthe ponies of this town,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to present\Nthe Cutie Mark Crusaders
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,with a three-handled\Nkey to the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.29,0:18:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A full Wonderbolt\Nsalute?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.42,0:18:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm not sure you\Nknow just how important
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.79,0:18:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Scootaloo and her friends\Nare, little brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.86,0:18:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're about to find out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.76,0:18:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The CMCs used their free\Ntime to set up a camp
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.77,0:18:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to help us blank flanks\Nfind our cutie marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:19:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The Cutie Mark Crusaders\Nsee the best in everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.87,0:19:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when that pony can't\Nsee it in themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.68,0:19:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be a\Nthree-tailed bandicoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea how important\NScoot's club was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's WAY more\Nthan just a club.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The CMCs have made a difference
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.22,0:19:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,for {\i1}everypony{\i0} here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And not just ponies!\NThey help everycreature.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.19,0:19:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it's encouraging others
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to discover their\Nspecial talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Or inspiring them to do\Nwhat's in their heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.57,0:19:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,These three fillies\Noffer the town
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.44,0:19:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,something no other pony can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.98,0:19:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! After all that, you're\Nstill gonna make her leave!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.02,0:19:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We just want what's\Nbest for Scootaloo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And until now...we thought\Nwe knew what that was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] Turns out, you're\Njust like us, Scoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.60,0:19:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You have an important\Njob that only you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You love it, and it\Nhelps all of Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes that means missing\Nout on other things you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.57,0:20:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Like watching our\Ndaughter grow into a pony
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.04,0:20:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,we're very proud of.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.11,0:20:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is a long way to say:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.38,0:20:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Scoot, if you want to\Nstay, we understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.29,0:20:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!? Thanks,\NDad! Thanks, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.12,0:20:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.90,0:20:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sweetie. I'm just sorry\Nwe didn't realize it sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Our work is our life's\Npurpose. We could never quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.87,0:20:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's no way we could\Nask you to do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.11,0:20:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should've\Nthought of that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.41,0:20:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,BEFORE you sold\Nthe house.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Lofty, don't tease my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We already have a\Nsolution worked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.49,0:20:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the CMCs make\NPonyville such a nice place,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.96,0:20:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,we've decided to move here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.69,0:21:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You can live with us,\NScootaloo. If you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you... still\Ncome and visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.27,0:21:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Rabid bugbears\Ncouldn't keep us away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.57,0:21:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You get to stay here!\NYou get to stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You get to stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.31,0:21:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, you ARE staying here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.75,0:21:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding? CMCs forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.79,0:21:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Woohoo!
